data.description: Charming Traditional Home in The Glen at Stone Oak! Welcome to this beautifully maintained 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath traditional style home nestled in the sought-after subdivision of The Glen at Stone Oak. Step inside and be greeted by a well-lit foyer that seamlessly leads to the heart of the home. The spacious living area boasts rich hardwood flooring and large windows, allowing for an abundance of natural light. The open-concept design ensures a smooth flow into the kitchen and dining area, with ample storage found in the beautiful cabinetry. All 4 bedrooms provide generous space and comfort. The master suite offers an en-suite bath complete with double vanity, a soaking tub, and a separate glass-enclosed shower. The remaining bedrooms are perfect for family, guests, or even a home office setup. Venture outside to the private backyard - ideal for hosting BBQs on the spacious patio or enjoying morning coffee on the covered patio. Additional features include a 2-car attached garage and a conveniently located laundry room. Located in The Glen at Stone Oak, residents benefit from a sense of community, top-rated schools, and proximity to local amenities, shopping, and dining. Enjoy peaceful neighborhood walks, nearby parks, and the overall tranquility this subdivision offers.
